;Room 402
NUMBER 149
 NAME Hotel Escapades, Room 402
 REGION 0
 INDOOR_FLOOR
 FIXED_LIGHT
 CHANNEL 1

*DESCRIPTION_START
The furnishings in this spartan room consist only of a simple bed, a dresser
and a nightstand. The stained carpets and dingy walls suggest that this room
has been kept for those who need minimal comforts.
*DESCRIPTION_END

 EXIT O 145
 ; Hallway door
 ITEM 0 350 VAL2=145 UNLOCKED
 ; Bed
 ITEM 1 74
 ; Nightstand
 ITEM 2 1401
 ; Dresser
 ITEM 3 1402

