;Room 403
NUMBER 150
 NAME Hotel Escapades, Room 403
 REGION 0
 INDOOR_FLOOR
 FIXED_LIGHT
 CHANNEL 1

*DESCRIPTION_START
From the gold carpet and bedspread to the gilt-framed paintings and wallpaper
of velvet and gold foil, this room has been decorated to give an impression of
wealth that doesn't seem to ring true. The king-sized bed sags slightly from
frequent use.
*DESCRIPTION_END

 EXIT O 146
 ; Hallway door
 ITEM 0 350 VAL2=146 UNLOCKED
 ; Bed
 ITEM 1 74
 ; Nightstand
 ITEM 2 1401
 ; Dresser
 ITEM 3 1402
 ; Mirror
 ITEM 4 657
 ; Chair
 ITEM 5 215 ADJ1=311

